{"type":"message","id":"431ac700","parentId":"30b02747","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:00:00.201Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Monday, May 11th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-05-11 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1778461200200}}
{"type":"message","id":"fab7328e","parentId":"431ac700","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:00:22.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job that fires daily to refresh the Cursor collaboration rules. The task says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" (no reply needed, silently confirm). So I just need to acknowledge and confirm the rules are remembered, then wrap up."},{"type":"text","text":"规则已确认记住。Cursor 协作流程：\n1. 提交任务用 `submit_task.py`\n2. 用户确认回复用 `confirm_write.py`\n3. 查看队列 `--list`，查看结果 `--results`\n\n静默确认，无需回复。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778461200201}}
